========================================================
Priority Scheduling
========================================================
Non-preemptive. Whenever the CPU becomes free, run the available process with the highest priority. Smaller priority number means higher priority.

Execution timeline:
  [ 0,  3)  P2
  [ 3,  6)  P3
  [ 6, 11)  P1
  [11, 18)  P4

